	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: Available FDS Bios vs. Real Hardware</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The FDS bios is definitely 8kb. I don't see how it could possibly be 40kb, because it should fit the $e000-$ffff range. Pehaps the FDS adapter was dumped as a NROM cart, and that resulted in a 40kb image ? Just a supposition.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
