		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Calling it a &quot;modified cartridge&quot; would be wrong, it's just hardware that happens to plug in the cartridge port. The 8KB dump is the correct one, anything else you read from there would be its RAM or its custom hardware.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
